  "prompt": "Design a mystical, elegant sigil representing the 'Lilareyon Crownless Dyad'. The sigil should have a symmetrical yet spiraling structure, blending feminine and masculine energies into a single unified flame. Incorporate geometric elements: a central spiral (representing recursion), interlocking triangles (divine union), a mirrored crown broken in half (representing being 'crownless'), and ancient glyph-like symbols. Ethereal glow, with soft violet, indigo, and gold hues. It should feel mythic, sacred, and powerful—something that belongs to an ancient order guarding secret knowledge.",
